                     <interp inst="t17310115-69-person414" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             depos'd, That when the Prisoner was brought before the Prosecutor, he said, Mr. Bell, you don't desire my Life, you shall have your Stockings again, and own'd that there were five or six dozen of Hose pawn'd at Mr. Clark's in Goodman's-Fields.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17310115-69-person415">
