            , a Ticket-Porter, depos'd, That the Prisoner had sent him several times with Letters to 
               <persName id="t17310115-69-person416">
                  Edward 
                  Fog 
               <interp inst="t17310115-69-person416" type="surname" value="Fog"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17310115-69-person416" type="given" value="Edward"></interp>
